Type: Package
Package: flotsam
Title: Finicky LOcal Tangent Space Alignment Method
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Melville", , "jlmelville@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Implements the Local Tangent Space Alignment (LTSA) method of
    Zhang and Zha (2004) <doi:10.1137/S1064827502419154> for nonlinear
    dimensionality reduction. Nearest-neighbor search and sparse eigensolvers
    are used to construct low-dimensional embeddings from local tangent space
    approximations.
License: GPL (>= 3)
